// Sprint 1 acceptance fixture: multi-error file with no parser cascade.
// Four independent failures separated by well-formed declarations. The
// parser must emit exactly one diagnostic per root cause (four total),
// with no extra diagnostics attributable to cascade. The well-formed
// declarations between the errors must appear in the AST as ordinary
// FnDecl nodes — proof the parser resumed cleanly each time.
fn first(): int { return 1 }

fn broken_expr(): int {
    return 2 +
}

fn second(): int { return 2 }

const := 5

fn third(): int { return 3 }

@@@

fn fourth(): int { return 4 }
